title: Here we go again
author: VD
content_html:
Mark Rosen reports Favre is unretiring. Again.

A high-level source with the Minnesota Vikings tells WCCO-TV’s Mark Rosen that quarterback Brett Favre is expected to sign with the team Tuesday.

I don’t even have an opinion at this point… fortunately, we Vikings fans have had a lifetime’s experience in being stoic. But, as my brother reminds me, Favre #1 and Sage #2 is without question better than Sage #1 and the Tarvaris Jackson Experiment #2.
content_text:
Mark Rosen reports
Favre is unretiring
.  Again.
A high-level source with the Minnesota Vikings tells WCCO-TV’s Mark Rosen that quarterback Brett Favre is expected to sign with the team Tuesday.
I don’t even have an opinion at this point… fortunately, we Vikings fans have had a lifetime’s experience in being stoic.  But, as my brother reminds me, Favre #1 and Sage #2 is without question better than Sage #1 and the Tarvaris Jackson Experiment #2.
